      • search

        java.util.List<Image> search(java.lang.String howToSearch,
                             java.lang.String howToOrder,
                             java.lang.String input)
        To search the images in the database.
        参数:
        howToSearch - Two options available, "title" and "content"
        howToOrder - Two options available, they're "time" and "popularity" In the first case, the result is sorted in a descendant chronicle order. In the second case, the result is sorted in a descendant popularity order.
        input - The input from the user
        返回:
        The image list that have been gotten.
